<resolution-body style="multiple-resolved-clause" id="H72227B5AA2F144659AA47163B42FB0C1"> 
<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="HB15836216DA44C2599E13CCCB926CC65"><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">That the House has heard with profound sorrow of the death of the Honorable David Scott, a Representative from the State of Georgia.</text></section> <section id="H3AAA41CD1561419D9AB0678ABE1BF39E" section-type="resolved"><text>That the Clerk communicate these resolutions to the Senate and transmit a copy thereof to the family of the deceased.</text></section>
<section id="H1CB023F0DDDA49D0ABEAFF74BC91F89B" section-type="resolved"><text>That when the House adjourns today, it adjourn as a further mark of respect to the memory of the deceased.</text></section> </resolution-body> <attestation><attestation-group><attestor display="no">Kevin F. McCumber,</attestor><role>Clerk.</role></attestation-group></attestation> </resolution> 

